strict court granted summary judgment in favor of the District. We have jurisdiction under 28 <mark>U</mark>.S.C. § 1291. Reviewing de novo,\n  \n   1\n  \n  we affirm.\n \n\n  I. TURNOUT GEAR\n \n', 'status': 'Precedential', 'suitNature': 'Civil', 'timestamp': '2025-10-24T17:03:51.666954-07:00', 'type': '010combined'}]}
